title: adidas Skateboarding The Rosewood Invitational
description: To celebrate the release of the Crush Pack, adidas Skateboarding and The Hundreds hosted the Rosewood Invitational, a soccer tournament featuring teams from the skateboarding and streetwear world. Watch Tim O’Connor recap all the highlights.
